verbose_text: At the molecular level, upregulation of SOCS, downregulation of peroxisome proliferator activated receptor (PPAR), increased proteasome activator 28gamma (PA28gamma) level, activation of the mTOR pathway and intense oxidative stress are suggested mechanisms implicated in disturbances in the insulin signaling pathway.
